\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch An Event located at a Time Code of 1,000,000,000 (1 Second Offset) on a Track positioned at Time Code of 20,000,000,000 (20 Second Offset) within the Composition would therefore be triggered at 21 seconds in to the play back of the composition.}{\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\par}
